<div><ul>
<li>300MW solar plant in Myanmar, the largest in ASEAN, acting for the sponsors</li>
<li>Assisting an international financial institution with its financing of a solar project in Cambodia</li>
<li>30MW wind farm in Myanmar for one of the largest Asian power producers</li>
<li>90MW biomass power facility in Kampot, Cambodia, acting for the sponsors</li>
</ul>
